Berkshire Boosts Marmon Stake to 80.2% in $1.5 Billion Deal

-- B y   D a n   K r a u t
-- 
2011-05-06T22:34:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/berkshire-boosts-marmon-stake-to-80-2-in-1-5-billion-deal.html
Warren Buffett ’s  Berkshire Hathaway
Inc. (BRK/A)  increased its stake in Marmon Holdings to 80.2 percent in
the first quarter.  Buffett’s firm built its holding by acquiring 16.5 percent
of Marmon for about $1.5 billion in cash in the period, Omaha,
Nebraska-based Berkshire said in a regulatory filing today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dan Kraut in  New York  at 
 dkraut2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  